#~ msgid ""
#~ "MongoDB provides :doc:`built-in roles "
#~ "</reference/built-in-roles>`, each with "
#~ "a dedicated purpose for a common "
#~ "use case. Examples include the "
#~ ":authrole:`read`, :authrole:`readWrite`, "
