#~ msgstr ""

# 3daa15f2fa3f4bcda9b1f65af3a48666
#~ msgid ""
#~ "An :doc:`action </reference/privilege-actions>` "
#~ "is a command or method the user"
#~ " is allowed to perform on the "
#~ "resource. A resource can have multiple"
